  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492640/extras/df4a88c64faee794dd4c190faf1f3fd7.poster.avif?t=1609675677\" width=620 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492640/extras/df4a88c64faee794dd4c190faf1f3fd7.webm?t=1609675677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492640/extras/df4a88c64faee794dd4c190faf1f3fd7.mp4?t=1609675677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Welcome to Mini Island!</strong><br><br>Mixx Island: Remix is a one small hold & Gun, boss Rush mini-game of Casual difficulty!<br>This beautiful place was built only for simple fun! Choose the character and difficulty level that best suits you and enjoy a short, simple but colorful boss rush minigame!<br><br><strong>More About & Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Casual difficulty<br></li><li> Hold & Gun and Boss Rush<br></li><li> Simple Hit & Dodge Style Action.<br></li><li> 4 types of 16 playable characters.<br></li><li> 10 stages with 40 boss fights.<br></li><li> Colorful and sparkling art graphics.<br></li><li> 30 minutes to 45 minutes playtime</li></ul>",
